<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>9094</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>19006</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>波比在去儿童中心的路上遇到了弗拉尼校长。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>19006</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>22197</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你好，波比。” 她说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>22197</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>25920</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我那天在超市遇到了你妈妈。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>25920</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>28928</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她很开朗，也很亲切。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>28928</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>33381</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>母亲节，你有什么特别的计划吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>33381</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>37530</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>波比咽了一口口水。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>37530</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>41920</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦。母亲节……是什么时候？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>41920</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>44920</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>弗拉尼校长哈哈大笑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>44920</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>50120</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是下个星期天，波比！你有12天的时间。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>50120</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>59378</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你一定能想出好礼物！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>59378</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>65995</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“也许我们在儿童中心会制作一些母亲节礼物。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>65995</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>69643</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>波比边开门边想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>69643</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>73761</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>雪莉老师正在做准备。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>73761</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>78084</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>波比问贾森他的母亲节计划。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>78083</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>82701</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我和爸爸会为她做一个蛋糕。” 贾森说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>82701</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>85545</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“怎么了？你要做什么呢？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>85545</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>89256</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>雪莉老师吹了吹哨子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>89256</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>93811</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“把你们的东西收起来，然后过来吧。” 她说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>93811</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>97967</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>雪莉老师把纸杯分给大家。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>97967</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>105092</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“今天我们要把这些纸杯变成花盆。” 雪莉老师说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>105092</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>111115</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们要怎么把它们变成花盆呢？” 莉琪很好奇。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>111115</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>116536</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们在里面种下花种！” 雪莉老师说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>116536</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>121224</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们种什么花呢？” 波比问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>121224</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>128677</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妈妈们都喜欢花。也许这可以成为一个礼物。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>128677</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>132319</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>雪莉老师举起一个袋子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>132319</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>138257</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“金盏花。” 她说。她给大家看一张图。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>138257</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>142343</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“金盏花有绿叶和黄花。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>142343</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>149398</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“给我妈妈刚好，你不觉得吗？” 波比小声对贾森说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>149398</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>154788</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“应该吧。送她个电子游戏怎么样？” 贾森说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>154788</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>163014</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“贾森，妈妈们喜欢巧克力，不喜欢电子游戏。” 莉琪说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>163014</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>166952</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>雪莉老师用铅笔敲敲桌子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>166952</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>171936</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“首先，用铅笔在纸杯底下穿一个孔。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>171936</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>177694</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这样，在我们浇水的时候，多余的水可以流出来。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>177694</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>181311</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“接着，我们在杯子里装土。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>181311</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>191135</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大家去那边装土吧。” 雪莉老师指着地上的箱子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>191135</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>197924</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“然后我们用手指挖个小洞，把种子放进去，对吗？” 莉琪说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>197924</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>201776</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她和妈妈一起种过花。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>201776</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>205754</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的！” 雪莉老师说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>205754</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>214465</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她给每个孩子几个种子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>214465</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>222418</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“然后我们给它们水和阳光，等它们长大！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>222418</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>227207</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“等它们长大？” 波比紧张地想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>227207</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>231730</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他忘记种子需要时间长大了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>231730</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>235074</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“雪莉老师？” 波比问，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>235074</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>239980</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“金盏花在母亲节之前会开花吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>239980</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>246613</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不会。需要一两个月才能长大呢。” 雪莉老师回答。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>246613</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>251043</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不好了……” 波比开始担心。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>251043</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>256800</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>现在，他没有东西可以在母亲节给妈妈了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>256800</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>262136</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我知道了！你在下个星期天先把花盆给你妈妈。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>262136</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>267784</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>等花开了，就好像又过了一次母亲节！” 尼娜说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>267784</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>280400</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>波比笑了。真是个好主意！就这样好了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>